snippet.title: Disney's Atlantis: The Lost Empire - Activity Centre PC Gameplay
snippet.description: Disney's Atlantis the Lost Empire - Activity Centre is a video game published in 2001 and based on the story of the animated film Atlantis the Lost Empire by Disney Interactive.
